name: CYLANCE PROTECT [Handled Threat: <%= threat %>]
description: CylancePROTECT has discovered a threat on a device and precautionary action has been taken, either in the form of quarantine for further investigation, clearing (removal from the device), or waiving (approval by an admin to run on the device).

name: CYLANCE PROTECT [Unhandled Abnormal Threat: <%= threat %>]
description: CylancePROTECT has discovered an abnormal threat on a device and no action has been taken on it.

name: CYLANCE PROTECT [Unhandled Unsafe Threat: <%= threat %>]
description: CylancePROTECT has discovered an unsafe threat on a device and no action has been taken on it.
